Title: Defender of the Flame
Description:
The Expedition forces face formidable adversaries.

Drawn like moths to our keyflames, creatures of all types are intent on snuffing out the light and thwarting our rebuilding efforts.

Please help us defeat two of the most menacing denizens that threaten our keyflames. Together, we can drive back this darkness.
ObjectivesText: Eliminate two rare creatures within the areas controlled by the keyflames.

Objectives.Text: Rare creatures slain that threaten the Keyflames
